data.description: PRICE REDUCTION! Uncover Historic New Orleans Elegance at 2236 Baronne Street. Step into the Enchanting World of this Historic Victorian Gem, a true Masterpiece built in 1870. With 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and 2585 square feet of living space, this New Orleans home is a blend of Timeless Charm and Modern Comfort. Immerse yourself in the Southern Charm of a bygone era with Original 10' Heart of Pine Wood Floors, Exquisite Winding Wooden Stairway, and Elegant Fireplaces. Floor to Ceiling Windows bathe the interior in Natural Light, creating a Warm and Inviting Atmosphere.  Dining Delights: Located just 3 blocks from St Charles Ave, you are surrounded by fantastic New Orleans Restaurants and perfectly positioned along the Mardi Gras Parade Route! This is more than a home; it's a Piece of New Orleans History waiting for you to call it your own. Don't let this Classic Beauty slip away. Call for your Private Tour today!
